content: "Create a surreal digital art portrait of a young man standing on a cliff, overlooking a vast, mystical landscape. The man is surrounded by a glowing aura and has a thoughtful expression on his face. Behind him, a swirling vortex opens up into a dreamlike world filled with swirling clouds and glowing, geometric shapes. Use a vibrant, psychedelic color palette and a style inspired by vaporwave art."
